  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: April 8, 2025</p>

  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>Glass Etching Notes ("we", "our", or "the app") is a mobile application created by Luuk Spronk, designed to help glass engraving artists document and manage their design ideas. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring transparency about how the app handles your information.</p>

  <h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
  <p>We do not collect any personal data from users. All notes and designs created in the app are stored locally on your device and are not uploaded or shared externally.</p>

  <h2>3. Access to Device Features</h2>
  <p>The app may request access to your device’s camera and photo library to allow you to attach reference images to your notes. This access is strictly local and used only for in-app functionality. We do not access or transmit any of this data outside the app.</p>

